      • addOffset

        public LLACoordinate addOffset(double bearing,
                               double distance)
        Add offset to the location. The offset is specified by the bearing and distance of the shortest path to the target location.Note that altitude of the resultant location is not updated, while timestamp and accuracy is copied from source location.
        Parameters:
        bearing - Bearing in degrees East of North
        distance - Distance in meters LLACoordinate representing new location.
